{"tid":1383442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［社區合作］可減少政府6.4億收入來源","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:00.000Z","uid":159280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f9ea42f3220a1910f37d73504d35948d11f7f9","tid":1383442,"uid":159280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"今日發夢，見到有差人喺違例泊車，見到司機有電話號碼留低，即刻打俾佢叫佢即刻走。<br />\n<br />\n眼見克警成條街抄左起碼10張牛肉乾，就喺度諗如果我打晒個10個電話就可以幫10個市民慳到$3200。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">守護社區你我有責！本人反對違例泊車！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港01 <br />\n<br />\n去年違泊發201萬張「牛肉乾」涉6.4億罰款　中西區車位減560個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/289535/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%81%95%E6%B3%8A%E7%99%BC201%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5-%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E4%B9%BE-%E6%B6%896-4%E5%84%84%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE-%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%BB%8A%E4%BD%8D%E6%B8%9B560%E5%80%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F289535%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%258A%25E7%2599%25BC201%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5-%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E4%25B9%25BE-%25E6%25B6%25896-4%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%25B8%259B560%25E5%2580%258B&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=7f8fce3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/289535/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%81%95%E6%B3%8A%E7%99%BC201%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5-%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E4%B9%BE-%E6%B6%896-4%E5%84%84%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE-%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E8%BB%8A%E4%BD%8D%E6%B8%9B560%E5%80%8B</a>"},{"pid":"5426faa8183c71143bb6ca692d35e03adede56ab","tid":1383442,"uid":159280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"希望各位市民可以減輕前線警察壓力，減少紙張使用，就係一個電話咁簡單"}]}